    <section address="Why AMDL?">
      <title>Why AMDL?</title>
      <content>
        <para>AMDL is acronym for Assistance Markdown Language. It's the bastard child of MAML and MD.</para>
      </content>
      <sections>
        <section address="Why not MAMDL?">
          <title>Why not MAMDL?</title>
          <content>
            <list class="nobullet">
              <listItem>
                <para>It isn't created by Microsoft.</para>
              </listItem>
            </list>
          </content>
        </section>
        <section address="Why not AML?">
          <title>Why not AML?</title>
          <content>
            <list class="nobullet">
              <listItem>
                <para>That's the MAML file extension.</para>
              </listItem>
            </list>
          </content>
        </section>
        <section address="Why not AMD?">
          <title>Why not AMD?</title>
          <content>
            <list class="nobullet">
              <listItem>
                <para>That one's taken as well.</para>
              </listItem>
            </list>
          </content>
        </section>
        <section address="Isn't AMDL also taken?">
          <title>Isn't AMDL also taken?</title>
